arge;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">卡池</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/102600_bf3cb3a1c1759893e39c34fdb132bdae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F102600_bf3cb3a1c1759893e39c34fdb132bdae.jpg&h=2fad93d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/102612_734df99b4f7da1db41eec752d7a5f777.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F102612_734df99b4f7da1db41eec752d7a5f777.jpg&h=82533bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新手教學</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>感謝 冥幣巴整合</strong><br />\n其實你想知咩新手資料???大部分巴哈都有<br />\n <br />\n1. 每日我建議新手打龜仙人、Satan武道會、雲上活動，之後去攞獎品<br />\n <br />\n2. 如果係升Rank嘅，我估大家現在都係以力隊為主，請趁現在3倍經驗解主線Easy解到21-1(目覚めたさきに)，之後再解到呢關最高難度，力隊超4悟打體波易到爆，順便刷綠石(打蘭芝同畢拉夫)換下新手角<br />\n <br />\n3. 如果係打覺醒料，可以去覺醒活動關打<br />\n <br />\n4. 升到D卡咁上下，請先去解超本氣果關，每日打潛力解放材料<br />\n(開放條件:<br />\nA. Rank 50以上<br />\nB.「超本気の超決戦」ステージ2.激突！超サイヤ人孫悟空のZ-HARD Clear)<br />\n <br />\n5. 3倍經驗完左可以去刷每日強襲角，知、速角優先，刷的意思係講每隻刷10隻刷到10技，再刷多隻5技放倉，準備以後解超強襲.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"539348d90c9d95b917dadca00587f50310983516","tid":411853,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">角色代號</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>感謝 格劍巴整合代號名單</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a0zctwo2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa0zctwo2&h=79e63ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong>舊代號名單 感謝 photomore 巴打整合 </strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F1